data.description: Well-maintained home in Cuthbert, GA!! The first floor of this home features a living room, dining room, 3 bedrooms, bathrooms, laundry area, 9ft ceilings, refinished original pine floors, quaint fireplaces, and shiplap walls. The second floor features ANOTHER bedroom, ANOTHER bathroom, living area, kitchen, and storage with a separate exterior entrance and an interior entrance. The home sits on almost an acre of land and is home to a few mature pecan trees. Call today for your private showing!
